(They would getting mostly the info on the outside of the ship. They 
won't be able to get the inside plans.  That is unless Brightblade is 
sending the info to Megatron, then they could obtain it as well. The 
info would be stored in the Console that DarkMouse used. Therefore 
obtainable.)


::Spears::

Too angry to be scared at the moment,"Yeah, let's fly." She started 
to walk down the hall.  She stopped, turned around and walked back to 
Striker. She looked at him for a sec.  She thought what she was about 
to do was stupid, but what the hell.  She stood next to him, gave him 
a quick peck on the cheek,"I'm sorry for slamming the door on you 
like that," she said rather quickly.  Then she turned and walked down 
the hall, almost jogging.

and 
> Skulletron are going to do. Phobia might have some of the ship 
scanned from 
> his visit, but the jammers would most-likely have prevented him 
from getting 
> more than half.
> 
> ::Striker::
> 
> Striker raises an eyebrow. Spears seemed to be holding in alot of 
anger. He 
> smiles. "We'll have enough time to get to the CF," he says, 
forgetting about 
> Spears' fear of heights, "I could fly us there."
> 
> He blinks, realizing what he'd just said, "Or we could walk," he 
quickly adds 
> on, hoping the first comment wouldn't drive Spears to panic.
